{"tid":377174,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[眼疾撚] 睇野有重影","createTime":"2017-08-27T14:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T03:08:08.000Z","uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02d44ed8ad8930316093f90db90dc5c73956bdb7","tid":377174,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:07:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟雙眼近視五百幾度，左眼有百幾度散光。<br />\n<br />\n兩年前配新眼鏡後發現左眼喺暗嘅環境睇光嘅野有重影，初初以為係眼鏡度數唔啱，兩個月後去眼鏡鋪重新配過情況依舊。<br />\n<br />\n然後再細心留意先發現唔戴眼鏡嗰陣都有同樣情況，但只要對眼瞇埋少少或者用手指輕輕撳住眼皮上半就冇事。<br />\n<br />\n眼鏡鋪解答唔到問題成因，自己膽心係錐形角膜於是半年前去左 理大護眼 做檢查。<br />\n視光師話唔係錐形角膜，亦唔知咩原因。<br />\n<br />\n但係對我日常生活構成影響，所以喺度問下有冇人試過類似情況，同埋我可以再去邊度做檢查？"},{"pid":"ceaccdd0ac09d568980d992653a5f8173b6bbd7c","tid":377174,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"a2a1d4917a4f1c571602bfa9008560e0e450ab9e","tid":377174,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"小心視網膜脫落喎"},{"pid":"a977dc8b3324c9e88fd7552e44f023112eaddc05","tid":377174,"uid":125382,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:14:18.000Z","msg":"個衰仔話睇野好矇，咁我就帶個仔去驗眼配眼鏡啦，點知驗完出黎乜事都冇，我就同佢講：[衰仔，你玩野呀！]佢話佢近排睇所有野都變得好慢。呢個時候，我就知 佢越黎越快"},{"pid":"055cf97f359d17a111bdb4c658fe2be536a8aa41","tid":377174,"uid":121966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:14:50.000Z","msg":"嚴重散光都會有呢個問題"},{"pid":"239b2f52625dcad4c237e64c4e28abd090085751","tid":377174,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小心視網膜脫落喎</blockquote><br />\n視光師話我係有呢個危機，但重影唔係病徵之一"},{"pid":"eded0c08a43b6e33aa38da92a0fcf3488d297cdd","tid":377174,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嚴重散光都會有呢個問題</blockquote><br />\n咁可唔可以透過眼鏡/激光矯視黎糾正？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 發現有人同我情況完全一樣：<br />\n<a href=\"https://webptt.com/m.aspx?n=bbs/optical/M.1447219762.A.1C0.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebptt.com%2Fm.aspx%3Fn%3Dbbs%2Foptical%2FM.1447219762.A.1C0.html&d=H2dqvVENTcqX0qiaRhYNcwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7ab96334\" target=\"_blank\">https://webptt.com/m.aspx?n=bbs/optical/M.1447219762.A.1C0.html</a>"},{"pid":"d58795d1488aa0abf388be05197793729900a555","tid":377174,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:46:15.000Z","msg":"啱啱醒起 理大護眼 話我左眼瞳孔比正常人大，唔知呢個係咪原因 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a204bf830338c6d98c63e74b5b790c289dc877","tid":377174,"uid":20407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，小弟雙眼近視五百幾度，左眼有百幾度散光。<br />\n<br />\n兩年前配新眼鏡後發現<span style=\"color: red;\">左眼喺暗嘅環境睇光嘅野有重影</span>，初初以為係眼鏡度數唔啱，兩個月後去眼鏡鋪重新配過情況依舊。<br />\n<br />\n然後再細心留意先發現唔戴眼鏡嗰陣都有同樣情況，但只要對眼瞇埋少少或者用手指輕輕撳住眼皮上半就冇事。<br />\n<br />\n眼鏡鋪解答唔到問題成因，自己膽心係錐形角膜於是半年前去左 理大護眼 做檢查。<br />\n視光師話唔係錐形角膜，亦唔知咩原因。<br />\n<br />\n但係對我日常生活構成影響，所以喺度問下有冇人試過類似情況，同埋我可以再去邊度做檢查？</blockquote><br />\n即係好似喺暗嘅房睇電話左眼會見到重影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b7fddad5d522f1ef95558552b6f5cf5065662f","tid":377174,"uid":20407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱醒起 理大護眼 話我左眼瞳孔比正常人大，唔知呢個係咪原因 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係左眼瞳孔比正常大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n右眼正常？"},{"pid":"6a29c41b3a024472dc38ff39e8a1f3d67aaaeeb6","tid":377174,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df81ff194a7185276df25a667794464879f46164","tid":377174,"uid":93633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"去養和搵范醫生/鄭醫生驗下<br />\n其實都係套餐價收一千鬆少少<br />\n醫生會幫你滴藥水同睇眼底<br />\n樓主有重影唔係小事來，拿拿睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"f8c0102979008e8d16dcd6b05232e4f9eb6e262b","tid":377174,"uid":45765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:14:56.000Z","msg":"去眼科專科睇啦<br />\n700-1200"},{"pid":"bf3cb82c0c5e0d4af486b6e37743f6aac684f9b6","tid":377174,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T22:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，小弟雙眼近視五百幾度，左眼有百幾度散光。<br />\n<br />\n兩年前配新眼鏡後發現<span style=\"color: red;\">左眼喺暗嘅環境睇光嘅野有重影</span>，初初以為係眼鏡度數唔啱，兩個月後去眼鏡鋪重新配過情況依舊。<br />\n<br />\n然後再細心留意先發現唔戴眼鏡嗰陣都有同樣情況，但只要對眼瞇埋少少或者用手指輕輕撳住眼皮上半就冇事。<br />\n<br />\n眼鏡鋪解答唔到問題成因，自己膽心係錐形角膜於是半年前去左 理大護眼 做檢查。<br />\n視光師話唔係錐形角膜，亦唔知咩原因。<br />\n<br />\n但係對我日常生活構成影響，所以喺度問下有冇人試過類似情況，同埋我可以再去邊度做檢查？</blockquote><br />\n即係好似喺暗嘅房睇電話左眼會見到重影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯，其實睇d 顏色對比大嘅野都有，<br />\n例如mac 個booting 畫面，黑底白蘋果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd397649ec250962b56950aaac99cec2f9a82ee6","tid":377174,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T22:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱醒起 理大護眼 話我左眼瞳孔比正常人大，唔知呢個係咪原因 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係左眼瞳孔比正常大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n右眼正常？</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"cb972dbb58415c4edc66fcac316853ae27f1cabe","tid":377174,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:40:51.000Z","msg":"錐形角膜撚lm"},{"pid":"46d8035e529f442c4f769a87907badbe99fb193f","tid":377174,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:46:11.000Z","msg":"有腫瘤壓住視覺神經"},{"pid":"cb8d62d5e9ee9f2359b7c0f3167d140340dcf3a2","tid":377174,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有腫瘤壓住視覺神經</blockquote><br />\ntvb 睇得太多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c693f668d423865ecbb959ebe70469d2b28325","tid":377174,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:17:47.000Z","msg":"雙眼focus落一隻手指既時候，後面景物有重影，係咪正常？"},{"pid":"04edb386243976ebc90aa9c222ab4c5cb42bd856","tid":377174,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雙眼focus落一隻手指既時候，後面景物有重影，係咪正常？</blockquote><br />\n好似唔會，最多後面濛左"},{"pid":"12bbced0fd8650d46e88bf22aecebf04b85ace5e","tid":377174,"uid":20407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，小弟雙眼近視五百幾度，左眼有百幾度散光。<br />\n<br />\n兩年前配新眼鏡後發現<span style=\"color: red;\">左眼喺暗嘅環境睇光嘅野有重影</span>，初初以為係眼鏡度數唔啱，兩個月後去眼鏡鋪重新配過情況依舊。<br />\n<br />\n然後再細心留意先發現唔戴眼鏡嗰陣都有同樣情況，但只要對眼瞇埋少少或者用手指輕輕撳住眼皮上半就冇事。<br />\n<br />\n眼鏡鋪解答唔到問題成因，自己膽心係錐形角膜於是半年前去左 理大護眼 做檢查。<br />\n視光師話唔係錐形角膜，亦唔知咩原因。<br />\n<br />\n但係對我日常生活構成影響，所以喺度問下有冇人試過類似情況，同埋我可以再去邊度做檢查？</blockquote><br />\n即係好似喺暗嘅房睇電話左眼會見到重影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯，其實睇d 顏色對比大嘅野都有，<br />\n例如mac 個booting 畫面，黑底白蘋果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n揞住左眼時右眼冇重影？<br />\n淨係左眼有？<br />\n擺個窿仔喺隻眼前面會唔會冇咁重影？"},{"pid":"b313edfbd8b8443aa061a7b6a02b92ecdf4208b2","tid":377174,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，小弟雙眼近視五百幾度，左眼有百幾度散光。<br />\n<br />\n兩年前配新眼鏡後發現<span style=\"color: red;\">左眼喺暗嘅環境睇光嘅野有重影</span>，初初以為係眼鏡度數唔啱，兩個月後去眼鏡鋪重新配過情況依舊。<br />\n<br />\n然後再細心留意先發現唔戴眼鏡嗰陣都有同樣情況，但只要對眼瞇埋少少或者用手指輕輕撳住眼皮上半就冇事。<br />\n<br />\n眼鏡鋪解答唔到問題成因，自己膽心係錐形角膜於是半年前去左 理大護眼 做檢查。<br />\n視光師話唔係錐形角膜，亦唔知咩原因。<br />\n<br />\n但係對我日常生活構成影響，所以喺度問下有冇人試過類似情況，同埋我可以再去邊度做檢查？</blockquote><br />\n即係好似喺暗嘅房睇電話左眼會見到重影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯，其實睇d 顏色對比大嘅野都有，<br />\n例如mac 個booting 畫面，黑底白蘋果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n揞住左眼時右眼冇重影？<br />\n淨係左眼有？<br />\n擺個窿仔喺隻眼前面會唔會冇咁重影？</blockquote><br />\n揞住左眼時右眼有少少重影，但真係好少好少，戴左眼鏡之後係完全冇；<br />\n但左眼就戴唔戴眼鏡都有；<br />\n啱啱試左搵張紙篤個窿，再透過個窿黎望，好似真係冇重影 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實好難試得真，因為我度數深，個窿要好細先夠清晰分到有冇重影，<br />\n但如果個窿太細，就算有重影都睇唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以結論係我間眼鏡鋪太廢，配兩次鏡都唔啱度數？<br />\n我今晚去第二間再配，睇下有冇好d 先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aea5d5e2323e91d0eee33f1e5a0d3f3d09e79f1","tid":377174,"uid":90000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"路過多口問問，<br />\n隻眼成日好攰，之前眼科check 過眼又睇埋眼底，又冇咩問題。其實會唔會係副眼鏡問題，想去理大驗清楚d 近視散光（700度近視150度散光），有冇伏？"},{"pid":"371b90b50407d1aca571a143a8e51d780a321d38","tid":377174,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"睇野有重影即刻去睇眼科啦!!!!!"},{"pid":"2ac4dcc28504c0240af8e4079f8a273d80efb33c","tid":377174,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>路過多口問問，<br />\n隻眼成日好攰，之前眼科check 過眼又睇埋眼底，又冇咩問題。其實會唔會係副眼鏡問題，想去理大驗清楚d 近視散光（700度近視150度散光），有冇伏？</blockquote><br />\n伏就冇伏嘅，我俾左六舊水check,<br />\n要滴眼藥水影眼底相嗰隻，都check 得ok 仔細，<br />\n個視光師都好有心機答我問題，不過條友好後生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然後生都一樣可以夠料la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}